<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="30Dec1917"><font color="red">30 December 1917</font>, <cite>Pound Letters</cite> (Ezra Pound to LR): For God&apos;s sake do something to cheer Quinn [re suppression over Lewis&apos;s Cantleman&apos;s] &hellip; imprudent to use the Rodker thing. Everything else looks safe enough to me, until we get to Joyce. Whom we have got to print. Suppression or no suppression.</div>
